ginal=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f5cbce163af81e1f8d424d758723fe11_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f5cbce163af81e1f8d424d758723fe11_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cbr\u003eStep 1: 哥猜变式-\"任意正整数n，要么哥猜成立要么哥猜不成立\"\u003cbr\u003e(原变式-n符合哥猜或\"一个显然结论\")\u003cbr\u003e该变式显然为真\u003cbr\u003eStep 2: 因为如果哥猜成立，哥猜不能不成立\u003cbr\u003e(原过程-狗屁不通写不出来，你能把6k+2写成6k+3-1是废话，但是这跟它能不能变式成哥猜形式有关系么？)\u003cbr\u003eStep 3: 所以根据变式，哥猜只能成立\u003cbr\u003eQED.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e显然，该证明可以推广到任何定理的证明\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e那么克雷研究所你那几个题还有几个没做出来的可以把奖金准备准备打到我卡上了*:ﾟ*｡⋆(*´◡`)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e经过我多年的研究才使我领会了这种精辟的证明思路，这不禁使我想到了当年唐三藏西天取经的艰难困苦，历经九九八十一难终于功德圆满，今年下半年……开机……希望……大家2019两开花！\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-79cac61a64d45d1d9f407a8652305ddc_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"220\" data-rawheight=\"179\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"220\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='220'%20height='179'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"220\" data-rawheight=\"179\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"220\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-79cac61a64d45d1d9f407a8652305ddc_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"奇文共赏-我证明了哥猜！ 本人深受\"证明\"天才般思路的启发，觉得此证明思路还可以进一步简化和推广。 Step 1: 哥猜变式-\"任意正整数n，要么哥猜成立要么哥猜不成立\" (原变式-n符合哥猜或\"一个显然结论\") 该变式显然为真 Step 2: 因为如果哥猜成立，哥猜不能…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":fal